funeral.

80
00:06:58,451 --> 00:07:00,385
- When was that?
- 1980.

81
00:07:01,754 --> 00:07:03,688
Same year Sam
was sentenced to die.

82
00:07:03,756 --> 00:07:07,157
- Yes, sir.
- Your father must have been
a very young man.

83
00:07:07,226 --> 00:07:10,491
Thirty-five years,
four months, six days.

84
00:07:15,468 --> 00:07:18,198
Perhaps I shouldn't
have asked.

85
00:07:18,271 --> 00:07:20,262
It's not a big deal.

86
00:07:20,339 --> 00:07:24,537
