uncovered, and you are not welcomed.

90
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,712
For one terrible moment,

91
00:07:35,788 --> 00:07:38,052
Sam Cayhall is gonna be the most
talked-about man in the country.

92
00:07:38,124 --> 00:07:40,251
Mr. Goodman, I've been living
with this case, one way or another,

93
00:07:40,326 --> 00:07:41,816
my whole life.

94
00:07:41,894 --> 00:07:44,764
